      <li class="grey"> <em> 11<sup>#</sup></em><b> <a href="home.php?mod=space&amp;uid=6495&amp;mobile=2" class="blue">逍遥第一剑</a></b> </li> 
      <li class="grey rela"> 2006-7-31 15:16:00</li> 
